pandamanagementsystem

Class productData

  • java.lang.Object
    • pandamanagementsystem.productData

  • public class productData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the data for a product in an inventory system. It includes information such as the product's ID, name, type, cost, quantity, and reorder level.
